Afropop musician, Skiibii is topping music charts across Nigeria with the remix of his latest single titled ‘Baddest Boy’ featuring Davido. The new remix sits on No 1 on Apple music’s Top 100 Nigeria and Apple Music Top 25: Lagos city charts. The previous, which was released late last year, sits on No 3 position respectively.   Elated Annie Idibia features in 2 Face’s new music…     Son of Hollywood actress Regina King commits suicide     I would be bringing a lot to Nigerian Idol 7- IK Osakioduwa   Also on Audiomack, it has garnered over 1.6 million streams since its release two days ago. - Advertisement - Visual for the remix featuring Davido is also doing amazing numbers on YouTube since its release. Skiibii Mayana whose real name is Abbey Elias made headlines when he faked his death in 2015. He also exited his former label Five Star Music to start his record label, More Grace Music in 2014. ‘Baddest Boy’ produced by Runcheck in 2021 is off Manya’s latest project, ‘God Is Bigger Than Man’ Extended Play(EP).